Adaptive Navigation Modes (ANM)

Canonical Maxim

“Don’t worship one compass. Change navigation to fit the terrain.”

Meta Principle

Reasoning is not one algorithm.

It is navigation through semantic terrain, where each navigation method is an operator optimized for a different landscape.

The highest-order skill is not mastering one navigator—it is knowing when to switch.

